  "description": "The third season of <i>Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu</i>. <br><br>\n\nA year has passed since Subaru’s victory at the Sanctuary. He savors a life of fulfillment while Emilia’s camp stands united for the royal selection—until a fateful letter arrives. Anastasia, a royal selection candidate, has invited Emilia to the Watergate City of Priestella. But as the party begins its journey, crisis stirs beneath the surface and Subaru meets a cruel fate once again.<br><br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll) <br><br>\n\n<i>Note: The first episode has an extended runtime of ~90 minutes, and received an early premiere at Anime Expo on July 5, 2024.</i>",
